			<div class="col" >
				<p>2. Choose room of interest from available options.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<img src="/images/home.png" style="width: 400px; height: 257px;">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col" >
				<p>3. Chat with other users within the same chat room.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<img src="/images/chatpage.png" style="width: 400px; height: 257px;">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col" style="width: 33.33%">
