			</div>
			<div class="col" style="width: 33.33%">
				<img src="/images/forgotpword.png" style="width: 400px;">
			</div>
			<div class="col" style="width: 33.33%">
				<img src="/images/securityq.png" style="width: 400px; height: 257px;">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col" >
				<p>5. After correctly answering security question, set new password.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<img src="/images/changepword.png" style="width: 400px; height: 257px;">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


